> Entertainment Earthquakes, elections and more dissected at New Yorker fest In this Oct. 2, 2015 photo released by The New Yorker Festival, actress Sigourney Weaver, left, talks with New Yorker Film Critic Anthony Lane at the 2015 New Yorker Festival in New York.
